==International relations==
===Twin towns — Sister cities===
Bački Petrovac is twinned with:
* Babušnica, Serbia
* Martin, Slovakia
* Nitra, Slovakia
* Ružomberok, Slovakia
* Stará Ľubovňa, Slovakia
* Vukovar, Croatia
* Kirchheim unter Teck, Germany

